beatbox.name: Beat Box
beatbox.SA1: Gain ENRAGE for 3/4/5 seconds when using a SPECIAL MOVE.
beatbox.SA2: Gain 15/20/25% BLOCKBUSTER METER when using a SPECIAL MOVE.

bassline.name: Bassline
bassline.SA1: On TAG IN, gain HEAVY REGEN and ARMOR for 5/7/10 seconds.
bassline.SA2: On TAG IN, gain 20/25/35% SUPER METER.

resonantevil.name: Resonant Evil
resonantevil.SA1: Getting HIT has a 10% chance to grant ARMOR for 5/7/10 seconds.
resonantevil.SA2: Gain a 5% chance on HIT to STUN opponent for 3/4/5 seconds if you have ARMOR

robocopy.name: Robocopy
robocopy.SA1: Defeating an opponent grants 2 stacks of ARMOR and ENRAGE for 5/7/10 seconds.

treblemaker.name: Treble Maker
treblemaker.SA1: Heal for 5/7/10% of your MAX HEALTH after every 10th COMBO HIT suffered.
treblemaker.SA2: BLOCKBUSTER damage is increased by 1/2/3% of your current HEALTH.

epicsax.name: Epic Sax
epicsax.SA1: Gain 1/2/3% damage bonus per COMBO HIT, up to 50%.
epicsax.SA2: Gain a random BUFF for every 20/15/10 COMBO HITS.

gijazz.name: G.I. Jazz
gijazz.SA1: Once per match, gain 3/4/5 stacks of REGEN for 10 seconds when falling below 25% HEALTH.

megasonic.name: Megasonic
megasonic.SA1: When blocking a HIT, reduce damage taken by 25/50/75% and gain ENRAGE for 5 seconds. One ENRAGE stack is removed on the next successful HIT.
megasonic.SA2: While benefitting from ENRAGE, 25/50/75% of the damage dealt is regained as HEALTH.

privatedick.name: Private Dick
privatedick.SA1: 5% chance on HIT to STUN opponent for 2/2.5/3 seconds.
privatedick.SA2: Gain a 25/35/50% RESISTANCE to all DEBUFFS.

dreamband.name: Dream Band
dreamband.SA1: MIRROR 1 opponent BUFF and reset its timer every 20/15/10 combo hits.
dreamband.SA2: When KNOCKED DOWN reset the timer of all active BUFFS and gain IMMUNITY for 10/12/15 seconds.

heavymetal.name: Heavy Metal
heavymetal.SA1: 10/12/15% chance to gain ARMOR for 5 seconds when HIT with a close-range attack (includes Blocking).
heavymetal.SA2: While benefitting from ARMOR, BLOCKBUSTERS deal 50/75/100% bonus damage.

coldstones.name: Cold Stones
coldstones.SA1: Throws have a 10/15/20% chance to inflict STUN on the enemy for 6 seconds.
coldstones.SA2: Inflict 25/35/50% bonus damage against an enemy that has STUN.

underdog.name: Underdog
underdog.SA1: Gain ARMOR for 10/12/15 seconds when inflicted with a DEBUFF
underdog.SA2: Gain HASTE for 10/12/15 seconds when inflicted with a DEBUFF

hypeman.name: Hype Man
hypeman.SA1: While in HYPE MODE, DRAIN the meter of all opponent BLOCKBUSTERS by 5/7/10% per landed HIT.
hypeman.SA2: When activating HYPE MODE, teammates in reserve gain 25/35/50% METER for all BLOCKBUSTERS.

numberone.name: Number One
numberone.SA1: Gain HASTE for 5/7/10 seconds on opponent TAG IN.
numberone.SA2: 25% chance on HIT to gain ENRAGE for 5/7/10 seconds if HASTED.

wrestlerx.name: Wrestler X
wrestlerx.SA1: Gain REGEN for 5/7/10 seconds for every 10% HEALTH lost.
wrestlerx.SA2: While in HYPE MODE, all HITS have a 15/20/25% chance to inflict BLEED for 5 seconds.

dragonbrawler.name: Dragon Brawler
dragonbrawler.SA1: Gain 3/4/5 stacks of PRECISION when activating HYPE, and gain 100% increased CRIT DAMAGE while in HYPE MODE.
dragonbrawler.SA2: Gain 25/35/50% meter for all BLOCKBUSTERS when defeating an opponent with a BLOCKBUSTER.

freedomfighter.name: Freedom Fighter
freedomfighter.SA1: While below 50% Health, inflict CRIPPLE and ARMOR BREAK for 5/7/10 seconds each when BLOCKING any normal HIT.
freedomfighter.SA2: When BLOCKING a BLOCKBUSTER attack, DISABLE opponent BLOCKBUSTERS for 10/12/15 seconds and inflict STUN for 4 seconds.

weekendwarrior.name: Weekend Warrior
weekendwarrior.SA1: Achieve max HYPE and gain HASTE for 10 seconds when Beowulf first drops below 25/35/50% HEALTH.
weekendwarrior.SA2: When activating HYPE MODE, remove all DEBUFFS and gain IMMUNITY, FINAL STAND, and HEAVY REGEN for 10/12/15 seconds.

wulfsbane.name: Wulfsbane
wulfsbane.SA1: THROWS have a 50% chance to inflict CRIPPLE and HEAL BLOCK for 5/7/10 seconds.
wulfsbane.SA2: Inflict 25/35/50% bonus damage against an enemy that is suffering from a DEBUFF.

darkmight.name: Dark Might
darkmight.SA1: Damage is increased by 25/35/50% for each teammate defeated.
darkmight.SA2: LEVEL 3 BLOCKBUSTERS have a 15/25/35% chance to instantly defeat enemies if Beowulf has less than 50% HEALTH.

snakebite.name: Snake Bite
snakebite.SA1: Gain 1/2/3 stacks of EVASION and 25% BLOCKBUSTER METER when activating HYPE MODE.
snakebite.SA2: Gain permanent HASTE and 3/4/5 stacks of BARRIER when defeating an opponent while in HYPE MODE.

headstrong.name: Headstrong
headstrong.SA1: THROWS have a 50% chance to inflict CRIPPLE for 4/5/7 seconds.
headstrong.SA2: Also inflict ARMOR BREAK for 4/5/7 seconds.

understudy.name: Understudy
understudy.SA1: Gain a 15/30/50% bonus to THROW damage.
understudy.SA2: Gain ARMOR for 10/12/15 seconds when THROWING an opponent.

bigtop.name: Big Top
bigtop.SA1: Once per match, RESURRECT with 10/25/50% HEALTH when defeated.
bigtop.SA2: RESURRECT with INVINCIBILITY and UNFLINCHING for 4/5/6 seconds.

graymatter.name: Gray Matter
graymatter.SA1: Start every match with 25/35/50% BLOCKBUSTER METER.
graymatter.SA2: Teammates start every match with 15/20/25% SUPER METER.

toadwarrior.name: Toad Warrior
toadwarrior.SA1: Gain 1/2/3% BLOCKBUSTER METER per second while near an opponent.
toadwarrior.SA2: Inflict 25/35/50% bonus damage while a BLOCKBUSTER is fully charged.

armedforces.name: Armed Forces
armedforces.SA1: Getting HIT has a 5% chance to grant ARMOR for 5/7/10 seconds.

brainfreeze.name: Brain Freeze
brainfreeze.SA1: ATTACK damage is increased by 1/2/3% of your CURRENT HEALTH.
brainfreeze.SA2: Damage inflicted by the opponent is reduced by 1/2/3% per opponent COMBO HIT.

criminalmind.name: Criminal Mind
criminalmind.SA1: Inflict DEATH MARK and gain THORNS for 5/7/10 seconds each when either Fighter deals at least 10% MAX HEALTH from a single HIT.
criminalmind.SA2: Opponents are inflicted with BLEED for 3/4/5 seconds when dashing while suffering from DEATH MARK.

harlequin.name: Harlequin
harlequin.SA1: SPECIAL MOVE damage is increased by 10/15/20% for all teammates.
harlequin.SA2: COOLDOWN for SPECIAL MOVES is reduced by 25/30/35% for all teammates.

heavyhanded.name: Heavy Handed
heavyhanded.SA1: Gain ENRAGE every 0.3/0.2/0.1 seconds while charging a CHARGE ATTACK. ENRAGE is removed after the next HIT.
heavyhanded.SA2: While reaching 5 stacks of ENRAGE, gain UNFLINCHING for 5/7/10 seconds. UNFLINCHING is removed after the next HIT.

starspangled.name: Star-Spangled
starspangled.SA1: Inflict ARMOR BREAK for 10/12/15 seconds when either Fighter breaks a THROW.
starspangled.SA2: 15/20/25% chance on HIT to inflict STUN for 5 seconds if the opponent is suffering ARMOR BREAK and is in the air.

nunsense.name: Nunsense
nunsense.SA1: When at an ELEMENTAL ADVANTAGE, gain 1/2/3 random BUFFS for 10 seconds any time the opponent gains a BUFF.
nunsense.SA2: When at an ELEMENTAL ADVANTAGE, inflict 1/2/3 random DEBUFFS for 10 seconds after suffering any DEBUFF.

sundaeschool.name: Sundae School
sundaeschool.SA1: When any teammate inflicts a DEBUFF (excluding STUN), increase its duration by 1/2/3 second(s).
sundaeschool.SA2: When any teammate suffers a DEBUFF (excluding STUN), reduce its duration by 1/2/3 second(s).

doublicious.name: Doublicious
doublicious.SA1: 10/15/25% chance on HIT to TRANSFER 1 BUFF from the opponent to yourself.
doublicious.SA2: 10/15/25% chance when HIT to TRANSFER 1 DEBUFF from yourself to the opponent.

mystmatch.name: Myst-Match
mystmatch.SA1: While sharing the opponent's same element, gain a 50/75/100% chance to MIRROR all of an opponent's BUFFS any time the opponent gains a BUFF.
mystmatch.SA2: Gain 1/2/3 stack(s) of PRECISION when a BUFF expires.

templetyrant.name: Temple Tyrant
templetyrant.SA1: When TRANSMUTING to an ELEMENTAL ADVANTAGE, heal for 15/20/25% HEALTH.
templetyrant.SA2: Gain a 25/35/50% chance to convert any DEBUFF into ARMOR and REGEN for 10 seconds when at an ELEMENTAL ADVANTAGE.

evergreenevil.name: Evergreen Evil
evergreenevil.SA1: 5/7/10% chance when HIT while not at an ELEMENTAL DISADVANTAGE to gain REGEN and THORNS for 5 seconds, and to remove all DEBUFFS.
evergreenevil.SA2: When Double or any teammate gains a BUFF, its duration is increased by 3/4/5 seconds and Double gains 5% BLOCKBUSTER METER.

immoralfiber.name: Immoral Fiber
immoralfiber.SA1: On DEATH, deal damage equivalent to 25/35/50% of your MAX HEALTH.
immoralfiber.SA2: On DEATH, heal all teammates by 25/35/50% of your MAX HEALTH.

rainbowblight.name: Rainbow Blight
rainbowblight.SA1: When TRANSMUTING, gain BUFFS based on the resulting ELEMENT for 5/7/10 seconds (Air: Heavy Regen, Fire: 2 Enrage, Water: 2 Armor, Dark: Haste, Light: Immunity).
rainbowblight.SA2: When TRANSMUTING, inflict DEBUFFS based on the resulting ELEMENT for 5/7/10 seconds (Air: Disable Blockbusters, Fire: Bleed, Water: Cripple, Dark: Heal Block, Light: Hex).

xenomorph.name: Xenomorph
xenomorph.SA1: 50/75/100% chance when TRANSMUTING to the DARK element to inflict a permanent DOOM effect, killing the enemy after 30 seconds. DOOM will be removed if Double is defeated.
xenomorph.SA2: On DEATH, inflict 1/2/3 stack of permanent BLEED.

heartofdarkness.name: Heart of Darkness
heartofdarkness.SA1: Once per match when TRANSMUTING to the opponent's element, permanently copy their Signature Ability and inflict HEX for 20/25/30 seconds.
heartofdarkness.SA2: 50/75/100% chance when Double's opponent TAGS OUT for all active opponent DEBUFFS to transfer to the incoming opponent.

jawbreaker.name: Jawbreaker
jawbreaker.SA1: When TRANSMUTING, gain a random BUFF for 5/6/7 seconds.
jawbreaker.SA2: Deal 10/15/20% bonus damage for each BUFF applied to Double.

decrypted.name: Decrypted
decrypted.SA1: Inflict 25/35/50% bonus damage against an opponent with BUFFS.
decrypted.SA2: Inflict 15/20/25% bonus damage for each of the opponents living teammates.

indenile.name: In Denile
indenile.SA1: Gain ARMOR for 5/10/15 seconds when triggering Sekhmet.
indenile.SA2: Remove all DEBUFFS and gain IMMUNITY for 5/10/15 seconds when triggering Sekhmet.

bloodyvalentine.name: Bloody Valentine
bloodyvalentine.SA1: Regain 5/10/15% HEALTH when either fighter uses a SPECIAL MOVE.
bloodyvalentine.SA2: Regain 5/10/15% SUPER METER when either fighter uses a BLOCKBUSTER.

scarletviper.name: Scarlet Viper
scarletviper.SA1: Inflict BLEED for 10/12/15 seconds on both fighters when triggering Sekhmet.
scarletviper.SA2: Gain ENRAGE for 10/12/15 seconds when suffering a DEBUFF.

tombandgloom.name: Tomb & Gloom
tombandgloom.SA1: Inflict WITHER, CURSE, HEALBLOCK, HEX, or DEATHMARK for 5/7/10 seconds when using a BLOCKBUSTER.
tombandgloom.SA2: Also gain 1 stack of EVASION for 5/7/10 seconds.

divaintervention.name: Diva Intervention
divaintervention.SA1: 25/35/50% of the damage inflicted by Sekhmet attacks is regained as HEALTH.
divaintervention.SA2: Sekhmet attacks drain 4/6/8% of the opponent's BLOCKBUSTER METER.

bloodbath.name: Bloodbath
bloodbath.SA1: If either fighter uses a BLOCKBUSTER, both fighters are afflicted with BLEED for 5/7/10 seconds.
bloodbath.SA2: 25/50/100% chance to convert all BLEED effects on self into REGEN.

redvelvet.name: Red Velvet
redvelvet.SA1: Inflict HEX for 10/12/15 seconds when triggering Sekhmet, disabling opponent SIGNATURE ABILITIES for the duration of the effect.
redvelvet.SA2: If an opponent TAGS OUT while suffering from HEX, the next opponent will be inflicted with 3 random DEBUFFS for 10/12/15 seconds.

lapisluxury.name: Lapis Luxury
lapisluxury.SA1: Once per match when TAGGING IN, match the meter value of the opponent's highest BLOCKBUSTER METER and inflict ARMOR BREAK for 10/12/15 seconds.
lapisluxury.SA2: Once per match when using a LEVEL 3 BLOCKBUSTER, switch HEALTH percentages with the opponent and gain HEAVY REGEN for 10/12/15 seconds.

innerpieces.name: Inner Pieces
innerpieces.SA1: When entering Sekhmet Mode, gain a BUFF for 10/12/15 seconds per teammate. The BUFF gained is determined by each teammate's ELEMENT.
innerpieces.SA2: 50/75/100% chance when TAGGING to or from Eliza for all active BUFFS to transfer to the incoming Fighter.

standout.name: Stand Out
standout.SA1: 50/60/75% of all damage is regained as HEALTH as long as Eliza's health percentage is lower than her opponent's (also applies on Blocked hits).
standout.SA2: Each BUFF gained by the opponent has a 25/35/50% chance to be removed and immediately build 25% meter for all of Eliza's BLOCKBUSTERS.

mummydearest.name: Mummy Dearest
mummydearest.SA1: Using a SPECIAL MOVE sacrifices 20% of all teammates' current HEALTH to gain 25/35/50% BLOCKBUSTER METER and HEAVY REGEN for 10 seconds.
mummydearest.SA2: Gain BLESSING for 20/25/30 seconds when entering SEKHMET MODE.

badhairday.name: Bad Hair Day
badhairday.SA1: 10% chance on HIT to inflict BLEED for 3/5/7 seconds.
badhairday.SA2: 10/12/15% bonus to CRIT RATE if opponent has BLEED.

frayedends.name: Frayed Ends
frayedends.SA1: 20% chance when HIT to inflict BLEED for 3/5/7 seconds.
frayedends.SA2: Inflict 25/35/50% bonus damage against an enemy with BLEED.

hairapparent.name: Hair Apparent
hairapparent.SA1: Using a SPECIAL MOVE grants HASTE for 10/12/15 seconds.
hairapparent.SA2: Using a BLOCKBUSTER has a 50/75/100% chance to reset the COOLDOWN of all SPECIAL MOVES.

rockstar.name: Rock Star
rockstar.SA1: While Filia is alive, all teammates TAG IN with 1/2/3 stacks of BARRIER for 10 seconds.
rockstar.SA2: When any teammate's BARRIER expires, they gain FINAL STAND for 10 seconds and 10/15/20% METER for all BLOCKBUSTERS.

parasiteweave.name: Parasite Weave
parasiteweave.SA1: 50% chance on CRITICAL HIT to inflict SLOW for 10 seconds and STUN for 2/2.5/3 seconds if the opponent is not already afflicted with SLOW.
parasiteweave.SA2: 5/10/15% chance on HIT to inflict BLEED for 5 seconds if opponent is STUNNED.

dreadlocks.name: Dread Locks
dreadlocks.SA1: When HIT, reflect 15/25/35% of the incoming damage.
dreadlocks.SA2: If the opponent lands a CRITICAL HIT, the opponent will receive HEAVY BLEED for 5/7/10 seconds.

windswept.name: Windswept
windswept.SA1: Gain a 25/35/50% chance to EVADE all projectiles, avoiding damage and hit reactions.
windswept.SA2: After EVADING, gain HASTE and ENRAGE for 5/7/10 seconds.

idolthreat.name: Idol Threat
idolthreat.SA1: EVADING an attack grants FINAL STAND and ARMOR for 5/7/10 seconds.
idolthreat.SA2: Inflict ARMOR BREAK for 5 seconds when HITTING a DASHING opponent. 100/150/200% of the damage inflicted is regained as HEALTH.

classcutter.name: Class Cutter
classcutter.SA1: All HITS from a BLOCKBUSTER or SPECIAL MOVE have a 10% chance to be UNBLOCKABLE and inflict DEATH MARK for 10/12/15 seconds.
classcutter.SA2: Inflict HEAVY BLEED and HEAL BLOCK for 10 seconds when dealing at least 10/7/5% of the opponent's MAX HEALTH from a single HIT.

djinnfrizz.name: Djinn Frizz
djinnfrizz.SA1: Every 20/15/10 seconds gain 3 random BUFF(S) for 5 seconds.
djinnfrizz.SA2: 33% chance when using a BLOCKBUSTER to convert 1/2/3 BUFF(S) into permanent ENRAGE.

justkitten.name: Just Kitten
justkitten.SA1: 25/35/50% chance when suffering a DEBUFF to immediately convert that DEBUFF to a stack of PRECISION.
justkitten.SA2: 5/10/15% chance on any non-projectile HIT to gain 1 stack of EVASION and HASTE for 10 seconds.

hellcat.name: Hellcat
hellcat.SA1: Gain permanent ENRAGE while HP is above 75/65/50%.
hellcat.SA2: Gain 3/4/5 stacks of PRECISION when defeating an opponent while benefiting from ENRAGE.

felinelucky.name: Feline Lucky
felinelucky.SA2: 2% chance on CRITICAL HIT to gain IMMUNE, INVINCIBLE, FINAL STAND, and UNFLINCHING for 15/20/25 seconds.

purrfectdark.name: Purrfect Dark
purrfectdark.SA1: After 15/12/10 seconds of facing Ms Fortune, the opponent suffers DEATH MARK and CURSE.
purrfectdark.SA2: HEAD HITS have a 10% chance to instantly defeat enemies if they are suffering from DEATH MARK and are below 25/35/50% HEALTH.

mstrial.name: Ms. Trial
mstrial.SA1: When HITTING a DASHING opponent, remove 1 of the opponent's BUFFS and gain 3/4/5 stacks of PRECISION.
mstrial.SA2: PRECISION HITS have a 50/75/100% chance to ignore the opponent's DEFENSE and ARMOR.

clawandorder.name: Claw & Order
clawandorder.SA1: CRITICAL HITS have a 25/35/50% chance to reset the timers of all opponent DEBUFFS except STUN and DOOM.
clawandorder.SA2: Set the opponent's SPECIAL MOVES on cooldown and DISABLE their BLOCKBUSTERS for 10/12/15 seconds when dealing at least 10/7/5% of the opponent's MAX HEALTH from a single HIT.

meowandfurever.name: Meow & Furever
meowandfurever.SA1: Gain FINAL STAND for 10 seconds and 3/4/5 Stacks of PRECISION for every 10% HEALTH LOST.
meowandfurever.SA2: Enemy is inflicted with DEATH MARK for 10/12/15 seconds and STUN for 4 seconds when FINAL STAND expires.

hacknsplash.name: Hack n' Splash
hacknsplash.SA1: A well-timed BLOCK against standard attacks grants 3/4/5 stacks of PRECISION and inflicts CRIPPLE and ARMOR BREAK for 10 seconds.
hacknsplash.SA2: Landing CRITICAL HITS with Ms. Fortune's HEAD deal an additional 1/2/3% of the opponent's MAX HEALTH if they are inflicted with CRIPPLE.

rogueagent.name: Rogue Agent
rogueagent.SA1: Each HEAD HIT has a 25% chance to TRANSFER 1 opponent BUFF and convert it into 1/2/3 stack(s) of PRECISION.
rogueagent.SA2: PRECISION HITS grant EVASION and inflict DEATH MARK for 5/7/10 seconds. Each stack of EVASION is removed after an evaded HIT.

furryfury.name: Furry Fury
furryfury.SA1: HEAD HITS have a 15% chance to inflict BLEED for 5/7/10 seconds.
furryfury.SA2: Gain ENRAGE every 3/2/1 second(s) while near an opponent suffering BLEED. The ENRAGE is removed when no longer near the opponent.

windstalker.name: Wind Stalker
windstalker.SA1: While near Ms. Fortune's head, opponent's lose 3/4/5% BLOCKBUSTER METER per second.
windstalker.SA2: Inflict DEATHMARK, DISABLE TAG INS, and DOOM for 15 seconds each when an opponent's HEALTH drops below 25/30/35%. DOOM is removed if the opponent uses a BLOCKBUSTER.

scrub.name: Scrub
scrub.SA1: Instantly recover 15/20/25% HEALTH when TAGGING OUT.
scrub.SA2: Teammates in reserve regenrates SCRATCH DAMAGE and gain BLOCKBUSTER meter 50/75/100% faster.

icyhot.name: Icy Hot
icyhot.SA1: All teammates TAG IN with REGEN for 10/12/15 seconds.
icyhot.SA2: On TAG IN, all teammates gain 5/10/15% meter for all BLOCKBUSTERS.

graveyardshift.name: Graveyard Shift
graveyardshift.SA1: Valentine and all teammates gain HEAVY REGEN for 10/12/15 seconds when any fighter is defeated.
graveyardshift.SA2: 15% Chance on HIT to inflict CURSE and HEAL BLOCK for 5/7/10 seconds when benefitting from REGEN.

ohmai.name: Oh Mai
ohmai.SA1: Gain 2 stacks of ENRAGE for 15/17/20 seconds and gain 5 stacks of PRECISON after defeating an opponent.
ohmai.SA2: When any teammate is defeated, all remaining teammates gain 2 stacks ENRAGE for 7/10/15 seconds.

killjoy.name: Kill Joy
killjoy.SA1: Teammates gain permanent REGEN when first dropping below 25/35/50% HP at ELEMENTAL ADVANTAGE.
killjoy.SA2: Once per match on DEATH, RESURRECT all defeated teammates with 15/20/25% HP.

silentkill.name: Silent Kill
silentkill.SA1: 15/20/25% chance on HIT to remove all DEBUFFS from self.
silentkill.SA2: 15/20/25% chance on HIT to remove all BUFFS from opponent.

lasthope.name: Last Hope
lasthope.SA1: Once per match while Valentine is alive, teammates gain HEAVY REGEN for 5/7/10 seconds when dropping below 25% health.
lasthope.SA2: Once per match when defeated, RESURRECT with 15/25/50% HEALTH.

surgeongeneral.name: Surgeon General
surgeongeneral.SA1: While Valentine is alive, she gains a permanent ENRAGE every 60/45/30 seconds.
surgeongeneral.SA2: While Valentine is alive, she grants IMMUNE and HEAVY REGEN for 10/12/15 seconds to all teammates every 30 seconds.

pyrotechnique.name: Pyro-Technique
pyrotechnique.SA1: Inflict 2 stacks of WITHER for 5/7/10 seconds when HITTING an opponent with a CHARGE ATTACK.
pyrotechnique.SA2: Gain ENRAGE for 5/7/10 seconds when HITTING an opponent with a fully depleted BLOCKBUSTER.

assassinsgreed.name: Assassin's Greed
assassinsgreed.SA1: When the opponent uses a BLOCKBUSTER against Valentine, they lose 15/20/25% of their remaining HEALTH and suffer HEAVY BLEED for 5 seconds.
assassinsgreed.SA2: Gain 3/4/5% HEALTH per second while nearby an opponent suffering BLEED.

treschic.name: Trés Chic
treschic.SA1: While on her own side of the stage, Valentine gains 1 stack of BARRIER, THORNS or ARMOR every 5/4/3 seconds. These BUFFS are removed when KNOCKED DOWN.
treschic.SA2: While on the opponent's side of the stage, CRITICAL HITS inflict BLEED, DEATH MARK, or ARMOR BREAK for 5/7/10 seconds.

rerun.name: Rerun
rerun.SA1: All teammates TAG IN with ENRAGE for 10/12/15 seconds.
rerun.SA2: COOLDOWN for TAG INS reduced by 25/35/50% for all teammates.

sketchy.name: Sketchy
sketchy.SA1: While peacock is alive, all teammates TAG IN with HASTE and IMMUNITY for 5/7/10 seconds (except after teammate death).
sketchy.SA2: While peacock is alive, All opponents TAG IN with SLOW and CURSE for 5/7/10 seconds (except after teammate death).

peashooter.name: Pea Shooter
peashooter.SA1: Projectiles inflict 15/25/35% more damage for all teammates.
peashooter.SA2: All projectiles have a 10/15% chance to inflict ARMOR BREAK for 3/6 seconds.

inkling.name: Inkling
inkling.SA1: Inflict 15/20/25% bonus damage for each living teammate.
inkling.SA2: SPECIAL MOVES have a 15/20/25% chance to be UNBLOCKABLE while Peacock has living teammates.

wildcard.name: Wildcard
wildcard.SA1: Inflict a random DEBUFF for 3/4/5 seconds when using a SPECIAL MOVE.
wildcard.SA2: If the opponent is suffering a DEBUFF when Peacock is defeated, the opponent's HEALTH is reduced by 25/35/50%.

untouchable.name: Untouchable
untouchable.SA1: 5/10/15% chance on getting HIT to avoid all damage (also applies while blocking).

thatsallfolks.name: That's All Folks!
thatsallfolks.SA1: Getting HIT has a 15% chance to inflict ARMOR BREAK for 5/7/10 seconds and grant 3/4/5 stacks of PRECISION and 1 stack of EVASION.
thatsallfolks.SA2: While Peacock is alive, enemies have 50/60/75% reduced CRIT RATE.

ultraviolent.name: Ultraviolent
ultraviolent.SA1: Projectiles have a 25/35/50% chance to ignore the opponent's DEFENSE and ARMOR.
ultraviolent.SA2: Projectiles inflict 25/35/50% more damage against opponents with UNFLINCHING or ARMOR.

meanone.name: Mean One
meanone.SA1: Gain ENRAGE for 10/12/15 seconds for every BUFF gained by the opponent.
meanone.SA2: Projectiles have a 25/35/50% chance on HIT to convert 1 opponent BUFF into a random DEBUFF.

freezeframe.name: Freeze Frame
freezeframe.SA1: Projectiles have a 25/35/50% chance to inflict SLOW and WITHER for 15 seconds. Both effects are removed if the opponent uses a BLOCKBUSTER.
freezeframe.SA2: When SLOW or WITHER expires, the opponent suffers damage equal to 25/35/50% of Peacock's ATTACK and is STUNNED for 3 seconds.

dreamcatcher.name: Dream Catcher
dreamcatcher.SA1: SPECIAL MOVES and TAG INS have a 25% chance on HIT to STUN the opponent for 4/5/6 seconds (does not affect Dark Fighters).
dreamcatcher.SA2: Every 3/2/1 second(s) while facing a STUNNED opponent, Peacock gains 1 stack of PRECISION and her teammates gain 5% BLOCKBUSTER METER, and 5% HEALTH.

sheltered.name: Sheltered
sheltered.SA1: Increases CRIT RATE by 10/15/20% for all teammates.
sheltered.SA2: On CRITICAL HIT, gain ENRAGE for 5/6/7 seconds.

heavyreign.name: Heavy Reign
heavyreign.SA1: 50% chance on CRITICAL HIT, gain 10/12/15% meter for all BLOCKBUSTERS.
heavyreign.SA2: 50% chance to gain 10/12/15% meter for all BLOCKBUSTERS when suffering a CRITICAL HIT.

noegrets.name: No Egrets
noegrets.SA1: On CRITICAL HIT, disable opponent's BLOCKBUSTERS for 2/3/4 seconds.
noegrets.SA2: Also disable SPECIAL MOVES and TAG INS for 2/3/4 seconds.

ivyleague.name: Ivy League
ivyleague.SA1: SLOW opponent's BLOCKBUSTERS for 5/7/10 seconds when spawning a TEAR.
ivyleague.SA2: On TEAR DETONATION, inflicts WITHER for 5/7/10 seconds per active TEAR.

shadowops.name: Shadow Ops
shadowops.SA1: Opponents suffer CURSE after 3/2/1 seconds while near a TEAR.
shadowops.SA2: Gain THORNS every 3/2/1 seconds while near a TEAR.

primed.name: Primed
primed.SA1: Gain ENRAGE for 5/7/10 seconds when spawning a TEAR.
primed.SA2: Detonated TEARS inflict BLEED for 3/4/5 seconds on HIT.

princesspride.name: Princess Pride
princesspride.SA1: Gain REGEN for 4/5/6 seconds when spawning a TEAR.
princesspride.SA2: On TEAR DETONATION, immediately recover 2/4/6% HEALTH per active TEAR.

regallyblonde.name: Regally Blonde
regallyblonde.SA1: When an opponent uses a BLOCKBUSTER, there is a 50% chance that their remaining BLOCKBUSTER METERS are reduced by 50/60/75%.
regallyblonde.SA2: On TEAR DETONATION, each active tear DISABLES opponent SPECIAL MOVES, BLOCKBUSTERS, or TAG INS for 5/6/8 seconds.

starcrossed.name: Star-Crossed
starcrossed.SA1: A well-timed BLOCK against standard attacks has a 50% chance to STUN the enemy for 1/2/3 seconds.
starcrossed.SA2: BLOCKBUSTERS inflict 50/75/100% bonus damage against STUNNED enemies.

summersalt.name: Summer Salt
summersalt.SA1: Opponents lose 1 BUFF and 1/2/3% HEALTH every 2 seconds while near a TEAR.
summersalt.SA2: When DETONATING at least 3 TEARS at once, REMOVE all DEBUFFS and gain 3/4/5 stacks of PRECISION. The detonated TEARS also deal 100% BONUS DAMAGE.

riskyginger.name: Risky Ginger
riskyginger.SA1: Inflict DEATH MARK for 10/12/15 seconds and gain ENRAGE when HITTING a DASHING opponent. A stack of ENRAGE is removed after each BLOCKED HIT.
riskyginger.SA2: With at least 5/4/3 stacks of ENRAGE, BLOCKBUSTERS become UNBLOCKABLE.

rusty.name: Rusty
rusty.SA1: 5/7/10% chance on HIT to inflict BLEED for 3 seconds.
rusty.SA2: Also converts 1/2/3 enemy BUFF(S) to BLEED.

twistedmettle.name: Twisted Mettle
twistedmettle.SA1: When suffering a CRITICAL HIT, inflict BLEED for 10/12/15 seconds.
twistedmettle.SA2: 25/35/50% chance on HIT to inflict BLEED for 3 seconds if opponent has BLEED.

blooddrive.name: Blood Drive
blooddrive.SA1: 5% chance on HIT to inflict BLEED on self and HEAVY BLEED on opponent for 5/7/10 seconds.
blooddrive.SA2: Gain ENRAGE for 4/5/6 seconds for every BLEED effect applied to Painwheel.

rageappropriate.name: Rage Appropriate
rageappropriate.SA1: Gain permanent ENRAGE every time an opponent's attack inflicts more than 15/13/10% total HEALTH.
rageappropriate.SA2: Once per match, gain HEAVY REGEN and 2 stacks of ARMOR for 10 seconds when HEALTH drops below 20/35/50%.

freakyfriday.name: Freaky Friday
freakyfriday.SA1: CRITICAL HITS inflict BLEED and DEATH MARK for 3/4/5 seconds each.
freakyfriday.SA2: Gain HASTE for 10 seconds and 3/4/5 stacks of PRECISION when defeating an opponent with a single HIT that deals at least 10% HEALTH.

rawnerv.name: Raw Nerv
rawnerv.SA1: Gain permanent ENRAGE and HASTE when your HEALTH drops below 25/35/50%.
rawnerv.SA2: Inflict permanent DEATH MARK when your HEALTH drops below 15/20/25%.

buzzkill.name: Buzzkill
buzzkill.SA1: 10% chance on HIT to inflict HEAVY BLEED for 5/7/10 seconds.
buzzkill.SA2: Gain permanent ENRAGE when an opponent's HEALTH drops below 15/20/25%.

firefly.name: Firefly
firefly.SA1: When blocking while below 50% HEALTH, gain 5/6/8% HEALTH per second.
firefly.SA2: Signature Ability 2 Also gain 5/6/8% BLOCKBUSTER METER per second.

grimfan.name: Grim Fan
grimfan.SA1: Once per match, gain UNFLINCHING and IMMUNITY for 15 seconds when dropping below 25/35/50% HEALTH.
grimfan.SA2: When Painwheel's UNFLINCHING expires, RESURRECT teammates with 20/25/30% HEALTH.

flytrap.name: Fly Trap
flytrap.SA1: Deal 15/20/25% bonus damage for each defeated Fighter, teammate or opponent.
flytrap.SA2: Gain 3/4/5 stacks of REGEN after defeating an opponent.

neuromancer.name: Neuromancer
neuromancer.SA1: Drain 5/7/10% BLOCKBUSTER METER for each non-BLOCKBUSTER HIT blocked by the opponent.
neuromancer.SA2: 10/12/15% of damage dealt from a BLOCKBUSTER is also suffered by the opponent's teammates.

stagefright.name: Stage Fright
stagefright.SA1: While facing Squigly, the opponent is afflicted with CURSE and HEX for 10/12/15 seconds when dropping below 25% HEALTH.
stagefright.SA2: Inflict a 30/25/20 second DOOM when defeated with a BLOCKBUSTER.

scaredstiff.name: Scared Stiff
scaredstiff.SA1: Gain UNFLINCHING for 5/7/10 seconds every 30 seconds.
scaredstiff.SA2: Cannot suffer more than 15/10/5% HEALTH from a single HIT.

nearlydeparted.name: Nearly Departed
nearlydeparted.SA1: When using a BLOCKBUSTER with an ODD COMBO COUNT, gain INVINCIBILITY for 5/6/8 seconds.
nearlydeparted.SA2: If below 50% HEALTH, also RESURRECT teammates with 15/20/25% HEALTH.

deadheat.name: Dead Heat
deadheat.SA1: BLOCKBUSTERS and SPECIAL MOVES become UNBLOCKABLE while below 15/20/25% HEALTH.
deadheat.SA2: If your opponent has a fully charged BLOCKBUSTER and you do not, gain 1/2/3% BLOCKBUSTER METER per second.

necrobreaker.name: Necrobreaker
necrobreaker.SA1: Once per match when suffering a HIT that would be fatal, gain FINAL STAND for 5/7/10 seconds.
necrobreaker.SA2: Gain 5/6/8% HEALTH per second while charging WYRM'S TAIL.

poltergust.name: Poltergust
poltergust.SA1: BLOCKBUSTERS deal 50/75/100% bonus damage to opponents with a fully charged BLOCKBUSTER.
poltergust.SA2: When a BUFF on Squigly or the opponent expires, gain 15/20/25% METER for all BLOCKBUSTERS.

deadofwinter.name: Dead of Winter
deadofwinter.SA1: RESURRECT with 25% HEALTH and 5 stacks of ARMOR after being dead for 60/45/30 seconds. A stack of ARMOR is removed after every HIT suffered.
deadofwinter.SA2: Deal 50/75/100% bonus damage while benefitting from ARMOR.

bioexorcist.name: Bio-Exorcist
bioexorcist.SA1: With at least 1 DRAGON CHARGE and not BLOCKING, DRAIN 1/1.5/2% of a nearby opponent's HEALTH per second.
bioexorcist.SA2: While CHARGED, DRAIN 15/20/25% HEALTH from each living teammate when suffering a HIT that would be fatal.

thrillshrieker.name: Thrill Shrieker
thrillshrieker.SA1: 50/75/100% chance to gain ENRAGE when gaining a DRAGON CHARGE. Each ENRAGE is removed when a charge is spent.
thrillshrieker.SA2: The opponent suffers damage equal to 25/35/50% of their current HEALTH when tagging out while Squigly has ENRAGE.

lovecrafted.name: Love Crafted
lovecrafted.SA1: While near an opponent, DISABLE BLOCKBUSTERS and inflict HEAL BLOCK after 3/2/1 second(s).
lovecrafted.SA2: Every 10th COMBO HIT will land as a CRITICAL HIT, and will inflict DEATH MARK and HEAVY BLEED for 10/12/15 seconds.

plottwisted.name: Plot Twisted
plottwisted.SA1: Once per match, RESURRECT with 25/35/50% HEALTH. Also gain 5 random DEBUFFS for 10 seconds and 5 stacks of THORNS for 20 seconds.
plottwisted.SA2: Deal 25/35/50% bonus damage for each active DEBUFF stack applied to Squigly.

prototype.name: Prototype
prototype.SA1: BLOCKBUSTER HITS have a 15/20/25% chance to inflict POWER SURGE for 10 seconds.
prototype.SA2: When using a BLOCKBUSTER, gain 15/20/25% meter for all BLOCKBUSTERS.

m3ow.name: M-3OW
m3ow.SA1: HEADRONES deal 50/75/100% bonus damage while Robo-Fortune is far away from the oponent.
m3ow.SA2: Gain INVINCIBLE for 3/4/5 seconds when HIT while far away from the opponent.

nyanotech.name: Nyanotech
nyanotech.SA1: Gain BARRIER for 5/7/10 seconds when launching a HEADRONE.
nyanotech.SA2: While benefitting from BARRIER, gain a 50/75/100% chance when suffering a DEBUFF to immediately convert that DEBUFF to ENRAGE.

purrminator.name: Purrminator
purrminator.SA1: 10/12/15% chance to gain 1 stack of PRECISION and inflict DEATH MARK for 10 seconds when the opponent BLOCKS a HIT.
purrminator.SA2: Each CRITICAL HIT permanently increases DAMAGE by 1/2/3%.

bluebomber.name: Blue Bomber
bluebomber.SA1: All BEAM and ENERGY attacks have a 25% chance on HIT to inflict ARMOR BREAK for 3/4/5 seconds.
bluebomber.SA2: Gain 3/4/5 stack(s) of BARRIER when using a LEVEL 3 BLOCKBUSTER.

terrorbyte.name: Terror Byte
terrorbyte.SA1: Inflict SLOW and POWER SURGE for 5/7/10 seconds after every 5 seconds not suffering a hit (includes blocked hits).
terrorbyte.SA2: HEADRONE HITS inflict INVERSE POLARITY for 5/7/10 seconds, reversing the effects of all healing.

bluescreen.name: Blue Screen
bluescreen.SA1: Gain a stack of armor every 10/7/5 seconds. Armor is removed when KNOCKED DOWN.
bluescreen.SA2: On DEATH, instantly detonate and inflict 25/35/50% bonus damage for each stack of armor applied to Robo Fortune.

headhunter.name: Head Hunter
headhunter.SA1: Gain one stack of PRECISION every 1.5/1/0.5 seconds while BLOCKING and not being hit.
headhunter.SA2: With at least three stacks of PRECISION, all BEAM and ENERGY attacks are UNBLOCKABLE and inflict POWER SURGE for 10/12/15 seconds.

personaassistant.name: Persona Assistant
personaassistant.SA1: Every 30 seconds while Robo-Fortune is alive, she gains 3/4/5 stacks of PRECISION and 3/4/5 stacks of ENRAGE for 5 seconds. Her teammates also gain 1 stack of BLESSING and BARRIER.
personaassistant.SA2: 50/75/100% chance for DASH ATTACKS to be UNBLOCKABLE while benefitting from ENRAGE.

overclocked.name: Overclocked
overclocked.SA1: Gain PRECISION and BARRIER after every 5/4/3 seconds not suffering a hit (includes blocked hits).
overclocked.SA2: All attacks are UNBLOCKABLE while at 5/4/3 or more stacks of PRECISION, and 50% of incoming damage is reflected while at 5/4/3 or more stacks of BARRIER.

xbot.name: X-Bot
xbot.SA1: Gain PRECISION and inflict DEATH MARK after 3/2/1 second(s) while far away from the opponent.
xbot.SA2: Also gain BARRIER and heal for 3/4/5% HEALTH.
